 <!-- Cataphract Boots -->
		
	<ThingDef ParentName="ApparelMakeableBase">
		<defName>Footwear_CataphractBoots</defName>
		<label>Cataphract boots</label>
		<description>A pair of Cataphract armor boots, equipped with top of the line technology, they compete with most experimental models in terms of sheer protection and mobility. 
		
Near pinacle of today's technology, these boot's only competition remains experimental models currently in development and upcoming technologies. Heavy utilization of plasteel and hyperweave creates superlight weight and highly protective footwear, uranium filament variants are also available.

Developer's Note: Cataphract Boots were added as a direct solution towards the substancial -0.80 c/s move speed offset. Some may consider them broken or overpowered so I've made alternative "Experimental" Uranium fillament Cataphract boots that have lower move speed bonus for higher overall protection, more in style with the armor itself.</description>
